// ShipmentStatus values: PENDING, PICKED_UP, IN_TRANSIT, OUT_FOR_DELIVERY, DELIVERED, EXCEPTION, RETURNED
// OrderStatus values: PENDING, CONFIRMED, PROCESSING, SHIPPED, DELIVERED, CANCELLED, REFUNDED
